casebody.data:
People ex rel. Le Boutillier, Appellant, v. Gilroy, Commissioner, Respondent. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department April 14, 1892.) Action by the people on the relation of George Le Boutillier against Thomas F. Gilroy.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O’Brien and Andrews, JJ.

John Delahunty, for appellant. Geo. L. Sterling, for respondent.

No opinion. Order modified as to movables within street lines, and affirmed as to stoop and area.
